description: A physicist uses the laws of thermodynamics to describe romance and relationships, but his theories prove faulty when it comes to his own love life.

title: Naam Shabana
cast: Tapsee Pannu, Akshay Kumar, Manoj Bajpayee, Prithviraj Sukumaran, Danny Denzongpa, Anupam Kher, Zakir Hussain, Virendra Saxenda
description: A fiery young woman accepts help from a spy agency to avenge her lover's murder. In return, she must prove herself as one of their top recruits.

title: Qarib Qarib Singlle
cast: Irrfan Khan, Parvathy, Neha Dhupia, Pushtii Shakti, Luke Kenny, Siddharth Menon, Bajrangbali Singh, Brijendra Kala
description: After reluctantly joining a dating app, a 35-year-old widow accompanies an easygoing poet on a trip to visit three of his exes.

title: Spyder
cast: Mahesh Babu, Rakul Preet Singh, S.J. Surya, Bharath Srinivasan, Priyadarshi Pullikonda, RJ Balaji
description: When an Intelligence Bureau officer’s phone-tapping day job leads him to a serial killer, he must track down and thwart the murderer’s next steps.

title: Maria Bamford: The Special Special Special
cast: Maria Bamford, Wayne Federman, Jackie Kashian
description: Spend an evening with gleeful, oh-so-awkward Maria Bamford via her cozy, shot-at-home comedy special, which has a two-person audience: her parents.

title: Bert Kreischer: Secret Time
cast: Bert Kreischer
description: Shirtless comic Bert Kreischer relays personal secrets and stories about being a cool – if not always responsible – dad in this stand-up special.

title: One Last Shot
cast: Robb Wells, John Paul Tremblay, John Dunsworth
description: In this low-budget short film, two best buddies meet up for a night of booze-fueled fun before one of them moves to Vancouver.

title: The After Party
cast: Kyle Harvey, Harrison Holzer, Teyana Taylor, Shelley Hennig, Wiz Khalifa, Blair Underwood, Jordan Rock, Amin Joseph, Andy Buckley, Jamie Choi
description: An aspiring rapper and his best friend/manager have one night to bounce back from embarrassment and make their dreams of hip-hop stardom come true.

title: Bareilly Ki Barfi
cast: Ayushmann Khurrana, Kriti Sanon, Rajkummar Rao, Pankaj Tripathi, Seema Pahwa, Rohit Chaudhury, Swati Semwal
description: When she falls in love with the author of a novel she adores, bohemian Bitti enlists the help of a local printer to find her new object of affection.

title: Mersal
cast: Joseph Vijay, S.J. Surya, Kajal Aggarwal, Samantha Ruth Prabhu, Nithya Menon, Vadivelu, Sathyaraj
description: A detective arrests a doctor for crimes targeting medical professionals but later finds the real culprit in a tale of revenge, corruption and magic.

title: Mom
cast: Sridevi, Akshaye Khanna, Sajal Ali, Nawazuddin Siddiqui, Adnan Siddiqui, Pitobash, Abhimanyu Singh, Vikas Verma
description: After her stepdaughter is sexually assaulted at a party, a furious mother sets out to destroy the lives of the four perpetrators who walked away free.
